:BaseX a owl:NamedIndividual , :MetadataEntity , :XMLProcessor , :QueryProcessor ; rdfs:label "BaseX"@en ; owl:sameAs <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BaseX> ; rdfs:comment "XML database and XQuery processor"@en .
