:ApacheJena a owl:NamedIndividual , :MetadataEntity , :TripleStore , :Reasoner ; rdfs:label "Apache Jena"@en ; owl:sameAs <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apache_Jena> ; rdfs:comment "framework for RDF storage, SPARQL processing, and reasoning"@en .
:GraphDB a owl:NamedIndividual , :MetadataEntity , :TripleStore , :Reasoner ; rdfs:label "GraphDB"@en ; owl:sameAs <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GraphDB> ; rdfs:comment "semantic graph database with RDF storage and reasoning support"@en .
:EclipseModelingFramework a owl:NamedIndividual , :MetadataEntity , :ModelingWorkbench ; rdfs:label "Eclipse Modeling Framework"@en ; owl:sameAs <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eclipse_Modeling_Framework> ; rdfs:comment "modeling workbench for Ecore-based models and metamodels"@en .
